---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Terms &amp; Conditions — The Second Spring"
  description="Terms of use for The Second Spring perimenopause support platform."
>
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-container">
      <h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="legal-date">Last updated: June 2026</p>

      <p>By using The Second Spring website and services (thesecondspring.org), you agree to these Terms and Conditions. Please read them carefully.</p>

      <h2>1. About The Second Spring</h2>
      <p>The Second Spring is an information and support platform for women navigating perimenopause and menopause. We provide general health information, an AI-powered companion for guidance, and community features. We are based in India.</p>

      <h2>2. Not Medical Advice</h2>
      <p><strong>The content on this website — including the AI companion, blog articles, guides, and community posts — is for general information and educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment.</strong></p>
      <p>Always consult your doctor or a qualified healthcare professional regarding any medical condition or before making any health-related decision. Do not disregard professional medical advice or delay seeking it because of something you have read on this platform.</p>
      <p>In a medical emergency, call 112 (India national emergency number) or go to your nearest hospital immediately.</p>

      <h2>3. The AI Companion</h2>
      <p>Our AI companion is designed to provide general health information and emotional support. It:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Is not a doctor and cannot diagnose medical conditions</li>
        <li>Cannot prescribe medication or treatments</li>
        <li>May occasionally provide incomplete or inaccurate information — always verify important health information with a qualified professional</li>
        <li>Is not a crisis service — if you are in mental health distress, please call iCall at 9152987821 or the national emergency number 112</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. User Conduct</h2>
      <p>When using The Second Spring, you agree to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Use the platform only for lawful purposes</li>
        <li>Not share false, harmful, or misleading health information</li>
        <li>Respect other community members and their privacy</li>
        <li>Not attempt to reverse-engineer, scrape, or misuse the platform</li>
        <li>Not submit content that infringes on any intellectual property rights</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>All content on this website — including articles, guides, illustrations, and the AI companion — is the intellectual property of The Second Spring unless otherwise stated. You may share links to our content. You may not copy, reproduce, or republish our content without written permission.</p>

      <h2>6. Community Content</h2>
      <p>If you submit questions, stories, or comments to our community section, you grant us a non-exclusive licence to publish and display this content on our platform. You confirm that you own the rights to any content you submit and that it does not violate anyone's rights or applicable law.</p>
      <p>We reserve the right to remove any community content that violates these terms or our community guidelines, at our sole discretion.</p>

      <h2>7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, The Second Spring shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of, or inability to use, this platform or its content.</p>
      <p>We do not warrant that the platform will be error-free, uninterrupted, or free from viruses or other harmful components.</p>

      <h2>8. External Links</h2>
      <p>Our platform may contain links to third-party websites. These are provided for your convenience. We do not endorse and are not responsible for the content of external websites.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these Terms from time to time. We will indicate the date of the most recent update at the top of this page. Continued use of the platform after changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated Terms.</p>

      <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>These Terms are governed by the laws of India. Any disputes shall be subject to the jurisdiction of courts in India.</p>

      <h2>11. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any questions about these Terms, please contact us at:<br />
      <a href="mailto:thesecondspringofficial@gmail.com">thesecondspringofficial@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page { background: var(--bg, #F6FAF7); min-height: 60vh; padding: 4rem 1.25rem; }
  .legal-container { max-width: 740px; margin: 0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text, #0F2A1A); margin-bottom: .5rem; }
  .legal-date { font-size: .85rem; color: var(--text-muted, #6B8C78); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
  h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text, #0F2A1A); margin: 2rem 0 .6rem; }
  p { font-size: .97rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-secondary, #2D4A38); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  ul { padding-left: 1.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  li { font-size: .97rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-secondary, #2D4A38); margin-bottom: .35rem; }
  a { color: var(--green, #3D7A5F); text-decoration: underline; }
  a:hover { color: var(--green-dark, #1A3D2B); }
</style>
